text: The phone is forever not answered although the company have a receptionist sitting there (simply doing nothing). To make matter worst, the receptionist refuse to sign for deliveries - she comment she does not want to take responsibility (might as well sit at home and do not work). Please, as a receptionist, you are the first point of contact for the company, your unprofessional attitude reflect badly on BW Shipping.
Nice company in high floor with nice sea view.
